{"tid":1755323,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"林鄭媽媽：政府虛心聆聽市民意見並認真反思","createTime":"2019-11-25T13:57:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-26T01:57:51.000Z","uid":201669,"like":1,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"d1f6d28f8f169c5b03919c83c86f8851d41fdb3a","tid":1755323,"uid":201669,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T13:57:22.000Z","msg":"政府一方向高等法院遞交文件冊，要求推翻原訟庭裁定《禁蒙面法》違憲的决定，並希望獲批上訴許可。<br />\n<br />\n文件指出，政府在暴力亂局中有合理必要去應用《禁蒙面法》保障公民，而且《禁蒙面法》所限制的權利及自由屬有限度，不會限制參與合法集會的市民權利。<br />\n<br />\n另外，決定現時局勢是否符合「危害公安」的定義仍有很大斟酌餘地，希望上訴庭接受《禁蒙面法》在「 危害公安」局勢有增無減的情況屬必要，暴力示威增加前線警員的工作壓力，以及人手緊張，到處破壞及實施暴力行為人士的私隱權亦毋須被保障。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1494409-20191125.htm?archive_date=2019-11-25\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1494409-20191125.htm%3Farchive_date%3D2019-11-25&d=yZvzIFdj7oCTZXRWgogUmVYPZSwMlx1ag7qd%2FaAfmLs%3D&h=2e9f2d8b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1494409-20191125.htm%3Farchive_date%3D2019-11-25&h=dbb37622\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1494409-20191125.htm?archive_date=2019-11-25</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n麻煩大家聽日就開始黎明行動同開花<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/aoqDbdU\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/aoqDbdU</a><br />\n<br />\n正式宣佈1126黎明行動 三罷再開<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/eAJkqS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/eAJkqS</a>"},{"pid":"5719e7f7aaf17401357f2db1d19353dbfc774ed8","tid":1755323,"uid":209543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T13:58:29.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"cb20e5d5498a88ed9d45395b9cf4dd46e08107e1","tid":1755323,"uid"